(12, '<p style=\'margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:10.0pt;margin-left:0cm;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif;text-align:center;background:white;\'><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: #F00;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;\">International Scientific Conference&nbsp;</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;\">&lsquo;</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;\">Forestry: Bridge to the Future</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;\">&rsquo;</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;\"><br>\r\n  &nbsp;</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;\">6</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;\">&nbsp;</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;\">&ndash;</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;\">&nbsp;9 May 20</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;\">20</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;\">, Sofia, Bulgaria </span>- postponed to 5-8 May 2021</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\'margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:3.0pt;margin-left:0cm;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif;text-align:justify;background:white;\'><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;\">University of Forestry Sofia has the pleasure to invite you to participate in the International Scientific Conference&nbsp;&lsquo;Forestry: Bridge to the Future&rsquo;, which will take place on&nbsp;5&nbsp;&ndash;&nbsp;8 May 2021&nbsp;in Sofia, Bulgaria.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\'margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:3.0pt;margin-left:0cm;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif;text-align:justify;background:white;\'><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;\">The Organizing committee of the conference „Forestry – Bridge to the Future” decided to conduct the event in a hybrid format. Participants will have the choice of attending in person or virtually.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\'margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:3.0pt;margin-left:0cm;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif;text-align:justify;background:white;\'><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;\">The Conference is dedicated to the 95th Anniversary of higher forestry education in Bulgaria and is organized by the University of Forestry, Sofia and Faculty of Forestry.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\'margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:3.0pt;margin-left:0cm;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif;text-align:justify;background:white;\'><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;\">The Conference sessions will be focused to the following topics: Climate Policy and Forest Sustainability (main topic) and following additional topics: i) Forest Biology and Ecology; ii) Forest Operations and Wood Processing; iii) Forest Economics and Management.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\'margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:3.0pt;margin-left:0cm;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif;text-align:justify;background:white;\'><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;\">Key speakers:&nbsp;Valeriu-Norocel Nicolescu&nbsp;(Transilvania University of Brasov, Romania),&nbsp;Raffaele Spinelli&nbsp;(Italian National Research Council, Rome, Italy), Mart-Jan Schelhaas (Wageningen University &amp; Research, Netherlands),&nbsp;and&nbsp;Georgi Kostov&nbsp;(University of Forestry, Sofia, Bulgaria).</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\'margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:3.0pt;margin-left:0cm;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif;text-align:justify;background:white;\'><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;\">All information regarding the Conference and its facilities: registration, accommodation, payments, program, abstract submission can be found on the official conference web-site:&nbsp;</span><strong><u><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: blue;\"><a href=\"https://conf2020.forestry-ideas.info\">https://conf2020.forestry-ideas.info</a></span></u></strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\'margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:3.0pt;margin-left:0cm;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif;text-align:justify;background:white;\'><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;\"></a></span></u></strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\'margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:10.0pt;margin-left:0cm;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif;text-align:justify;background:white;\'><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;\">We shall look forward to meet you in Sofia in 2021.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\'margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:10.0pt;margin-left:0cm;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif;text-align:justify;background:white;\'><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;\">Kind regards,</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse;\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"width: 267.65pt;padding: 0cm 5.4pt;vertical-align: top;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"56.39810426540284%\">\r\n\r\n				<p style=\'margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:10.0pt;margin-left:0cm;line-height:115%;font-size:15px;font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif;\'><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">Prof. DSc. Ivan Iliev<br> Honorable Chairman of the Organizing Committee<br> Rector of the University of Forestry<br>Sofia, Bulgaria</span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"width: 207.05pt;padding: 0cm 5.4pt;vertical-align: top;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"43.60189573459716%\">\r\n\r\n				<p style=\'margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:10.0pt;margin-left:0cm;line-height:115%;font-size:15px;font-family:\"Calibri\",sans-serif;\'><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">Assoc. prof. Dr. Marius Dimitrov<br> Chairman of the Organizing Committee<br> Dean of the Faculty of Forestry<br>University of Forestry, Sofia, Bulgaria</span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><br></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><br></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><br></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><strong>International Scientific Conference &ldquo;Forestry: Bridge to the Future&rdquo;<br>7 - 9 May 2015, Sofia, Bulgaria</strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">University of Forestry Sofia has the pleasure to invite you to participate in the International Scientific Conference &ldquo;Forestry: Bridge to the Future&rdquo;, which will take place on 7 - 9 May 2015 in Sofia, Bulgaria.<br>The Conference is dedicated to the 90th Anniversary of higher forestry education in Bulgaria and is organized by the University of Forestry, Sofia and Faculty of Forestry.<br>The Conference sessions will be focused to the following topics: Impact of climate change on forest ecosystems, Adaptation strategies and mitigation, Forest health and protection, Disturbances and disturbance regimes in forests, Fires, windstorms and soil erosion, Forest-related and energy policies.<br>Eminent keynote speakers have confirmed their participation:&nbsp;<a href=\"http://ourenvironment.berkeley.edu/people_profiles/kevin-ohara/\">Kevin&nbsp;</a><a href=\"http://ourenvironment.berkeley.edu/people_profiles/kevin-ohara/\">O&#39;HARA</a> (University of California, Berkeley, CA, USA),&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.gip-ecofor.org/\">Jean-Luc PEYRON</a> (ECOFOR, France) and&nbsp;<a href=\"http://conf2015.forestry-ideas.info/main/confinfo/iv_raev.php\">Ivan RA</a><a href=\"http://conf2015.forestry-ideas.info/main/confinfo/iv_raev.php\">EV</a> (Forest Research Institute, Sofia, Bulgaria).<br>All information regarding the Conference and its facilities: registration, accommodation, payments, program, abstract submission can be found on the official conference web-site:&nbsp;<a href=\"http://conf2015.forestry-ideas.info/\">http://conf2015.forestry-ideas.info</a></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">We shall look forward to meet you in Sofia in 2015.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">Kind regards,</span></p>\r\n\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td valign=\"top\" width=\"331\">\r\n\r\n				<p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">Prof. Dr. Veselin Brezin<br>Chairman of the Organizing Committee<br>Rector of the University of Forestry<br>Sofia, Bulgaria</span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td valign=\"top\" width=\"331\">\r\n\r\n				<p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">Assoc. prof. Dr. Milko Milev<br>Vice-chairman of the Organizing Committee<br>Dean of the Faculty of Forestry<br>University of Forestry, Sofia, Bulgaria</span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n\r\n', '', '');
