tyle=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Trichkov </span></strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">- University of Forestry, Sofia, Bulgaria</span><br />\r\n					<span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Jozef </span><strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Viglasky </span></strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">- Technical University in Zvolen, Slovakia</span><br />\r\n					<span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> Yaoqi </span><strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Zhang </span></strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">- Auburn University, USA</span></p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Language Editors:</span></strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> Dilyanka </span><strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Bezlova</span></strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">, Alexander </span><strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Delkov</span></strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">, Yordanka </span><strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Ivanova</span></strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">, Stefka </span><strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Kitanova</span></strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">, Yulin </span><strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Tepeliev</span></strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">, </span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Petar </span><strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Zhelev</span></strong><br />\r\n					<span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> </span><strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Production</span></strong><strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> Editor:</span></strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> Magdelina </span><strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Bozhankova</span><br />\r\n					<span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> Technical Editor: </span></strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Toma </span><strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Tonchev </span></strong><br />\r\n					<span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> </span><strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Cover Design:</span></strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> Jordan</span><strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> Markov </span></strong></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td valign=\"top\" width=\"34%\">\r\n				<p align=\"center\">\r\n					<span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">To contact with us post to:</span></p>\r\n				<p align=\"center\">\r\n					<a href=\"http://www.ltu.bg/\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">University of Forestry</span></span></a><br />\r\n					<span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> </span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Forestry Ideas&nbsp;Journal</span><br />\r\n					<span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> 10&nbsp;Kliment&nbsp;Okhridski blvd.</span><br />\r\n					<span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> 1797 Sofia</span><br />\r\n					<span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> Bulgaria</span><br />\r\n					<span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> Editorial Board</span><br />\r\n					<span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> Phone: +359 2 862 28 54</span><br />\r\n					<span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> </span><a href=\"http://ltu.bg\" target=\"_top\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">http://ltu.bg</span></a></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n </div>\r\n'),
(2, '    <table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n      <tr>\r\n        <td colspan=\"2\"><p align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>The journal  “Forestry Ideas” is issued by the University  of Forestry in Sofia. It publishes scientific papers in the  field of forestry sciences, landscape architecture, ecology and environmental  protection.</p></td>\r\n      </tr>\r\n      <tr>\r\n        <td colspan=\"2\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n      </tr>\r\n      <tr>\r\n        <td colspan=\"2\"><p><strong>History</strong></p>\r\n          <p><br />\r\n        “Forestry Ideas” was  established as an organ of the Society of academic foresters - in 1932 and it was published until 1943. Its first and  longtime chief editor was prof. Vassil  Stoyanov. The four books issued per year contained mainly scientific  publications. Since 1939 “Forestry Ideas” and the journals “Forest Review” were press organs of the united organization the Society  of Foresters in Bulgaria. The journal was resumed in 1994 and it is issued by the Publishing House of the University of Forestry.</p></td>\r\n      </tr>\r\n      <tr id=\"tr_images_history\">\r\n        <td colspan=\"2\">\r\n        <a href=\"../../images/Old_Journal/big/lesovdska_misal_I.jpg\" rel=\"lightbox\" title=\"\"><img src=\"../../images/Old_Journal/tumb/lesovdska_misal_I.jpg\" width=\"68\" height=\"100\" /></a>\r\n        <a href=\"../../images/Old_Journal/big/lesovdska_misal_I_page2.jpg\" rel=\"lightbox\" title=\"\"><img src=\"../../images/Old_Journal/tumb/lesovdska_misal_I_page2.jpg\" width=\"66\" height=\"100\" /></a>\r\n        <a href=\"../../images/Old_Journal/big/lesovdska_misal_I_page3.jpg\" rel=\"lightbox\" title=\"\"><img src=\"../../images/Old_Journal/tumb/lesovdska_misal_I_page3.jpg\" width=\"67\" height=\"100\" /></a>\r\n        <a href=\"../../images/Old_Journal/big/lesovdska_misal_XII.jpg\" rel=\"lightbox\" title=\"\"><img src=\"../../images/Old_Journal/tumb/lesovdska_misal_XII.jpg\" width=\"68\" heig