(1, '1 - 2', '2008', 'Лесовъдска мисъл', 'Forestry Ideas', '<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\">ПРОУЧВАНИЯ ВЪРХУ РАСТЕЖА НА РАЗЛИЧНИ ПРОИЗХОДИ НА ОБИКНОВЕНА ЕЛА (ABIES ALBA MILL.) В ОПИТНИ ЕКОЛОГИЧНИ КУЛТУРИ ...................................................................................................................................3<br><em>Иван Евтимов, Величко Гагов</em></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\"><br>ФЛОРНИ ЕЛЕМЕНТИ И БИОЛОГИЧЕН СПЕКТЪР НА ГОРИ С ПРЕОБЛАДАВАНЕ НА КОСМАТ ДЪБ (QUERCUS PUBESCENSWILLD.)&#160; В ЗАПАДНИТЕ ГРАНИЧНИ ПЛАНИНИ ..............................12<br><em>Георги Гогушев</em></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\"><br>ВЪЗСТАНОВЯВАНЕ НА ОПОЖАРЕНИ ГОРСКИ ПЛОЩИ НА ТЕРИТОРИЯТА НА ДГС „ШИРОКА ЛЪКА”<br>И ДГС „ИВАЙЛОВГРАД” ...............................................................................................29<br><em>Красимира Петкова, Александър Ташев, Латинка Топалова-Жежиха</em></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\"><br>АНАЛИЗ И ОЦЕНКА НА ПОЖАРИТЕ И ПОЖАРНАТА ОПАСНОСТ В ГОРИТЕ .....................................................................................................................................30<br></span><em><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\">Кирил Любенов, Владимир Константинов</span></em></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\"><br>КИСЕЛ ДРЕНАЖ НА НАСИПНИ СУБСТРАТИ</span></span><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\"> ОТ ДОБИВ НА ОЛОВНО-ЦИНКОВА РУДА .......................................................................................................................................47<br><em>Росица Петрова</em></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\"><br>ПРОДУКТИВНОСТ НА ФЕРМЕРНО ОТГЛЕЖДАНИ ПОЛСКИ ЯРЕБИЦИ (PERDIX PERDIX L.) В ЗАВИСИМОСТ ОТ НЯКОИ ФАКТОРИ НА СРЕДАТА ..............................................................74<br></span><em><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\">Звезделин Миланов</span></em></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\"><br>ИЗСЛЕДВАНЕ НА РАБОТАТА НА МАЛОГАБАРИТЕН ОБЕЗКРИЛИТЕЛ ЗА ОБРАБОТКА НА СЕМЕНА ОТ<br>ЧЕРЕН БОР (PINUS NIGRA ARN.) И ОБИКНОВЕН СМЪРЧ (PICEA ABIES KARST.) ......................................................................................................................................79<br></span><em><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\">Константин Маринов, Димитър Ненов, Сотир Глушков</span></em></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\"><br>ЕКСПЕРИМЕНТАЛНИ МЕТОДИ ЗА ИЗСЛЕДВАНЕ НА ЕФЕКТА ОТ ТРОПОСФЕРЕН ОЗОН ВЪРХУ ГОРС- КИ ЕКОСИСТЕМИ ...........................................................................................................97<br></span><em><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\">Петя Първанова, Николина Цветкова, Св. Братанова-Дончева,Р. Фикова, Светослав Анев</span></em></span></p>', '<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\">INVESTIGATIONS IN THE SILVER FIR (ABIES ALBA MILL.) ECOLOGICAL EXPERIMENTAL PROVENANCE<br>AND PROGENIE TRIALS ..................................................................................................11<br>Ivan Evtimov, Velitchko Gagov</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\"><br>FLORISTIC ELEMENTS AND BIOLOGICAL SPECTRUM OF FORESTS DOMINATED BY PUBESCENT OAK (QUERCUS PUBESCENS WILLD.) IN THE WEST FRONTIER MOUNTAINS .............................20<br></span><em><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\">Georgi Gogushev</span></em></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\"><br>RESTORATION OF BURNED FOREST AREAS ON THE TERRITORY OF SHIROKA LAKA AND VAILOVGRAD FORESTRY ENTERPRISES ...............................................................................................21<br></span><em><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\">Krasimira Petkova, Alexander Tashev, Latinka Topalova-Rzerzycha</span></em></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\"><br>ANALYSIS AND ASSESSMENT OF FOREST FIRES AND FIRE HAZARD .....................................................................................................................................46<br></span><em><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\">Kiril Lyubenov, Vladimir Konstantinov</span></em></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\"><br>ACID ROCK DRAINAGE FROM SUBSTRATA OF PB-ZN ORE PRODUCTION ....................................................................................................................................73<br></span><em><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\">Rossitsa Petrova</span></em></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\"><br>PRODUCTIVITY OF FARM-REARED GREY PARTRIDGES (PERDIX PERDIX L.) IN RELATION WITH SOME ECOLOGICAL VARIABLES ...............................................................................................78<br></span><em><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\">Zvezdelin Milanov</span></em></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\"><br>EXPLORATION OF THE DEWINGING PROCESS ON BLACK PINE (PUNUS NIGRA ARN) AND NORWAY SPRUCE (PICEA ABIES KARST) SEEDS WITH SMALL DIMENSION DEWINGER ........................96<br></span><em><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\">Konstantin Marinov, Dimitar Nenov, Sotir Glushkov</span></em></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\"><br>EXPERIMENTAL METHODS FOR ASSESSMENT OF TROPOSPHERIC OZONE EFFECT ON FOREST ECOSYSTEMS .............................................................................................................112<br></span><em><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\">P. Parvanova, N. T.zvetkova, Sv. Bratanova-Doncheva, R. Fikova, Sv. Anev</span></em></span></p>', '1-2_2008.pdf', 4, '14'),
